reviewText: It provides an excellent look at a rare intersection of eco-friendly and entrepreneurship, but the videographers' bias toward pro-market, anti-regulation was a little disarming. Nevertheless, I'll probably show it to my APES students again next year. (Btw, the order was fine - on time and in good shape.)
Excellent lesson for my students and the disk was in great shape . . . thanks!
Good info on how the free market can make anybody wealthy!!
